Wracked by insomnia and wanderlust, Kou Yamori is driven onto the moonlit streets every night in an aimless search for something he cant seem to name. His nightly ritual is marked by purposeless introspection until he meets Nazuna, who might just be a vampire! Kous new companion could offer him dark gifts and a vampires immortality. But there are conditions that must be met before Kou can sink his teeth into vampirism, and hell have to discover just how far hes willing to go to satisfy his desires before he can heed the Call of the Night!
(Source: Sentai Filmworks)
Dungeon Meshi: Senshi no Kantan Cooking!

Stop-motion short in honor of the 5th tankoubon going on sale. It features Senshi's hands trying to prepare a walking mushroom. It is the same walking mushroom as shown in the manga's 1st volume in the "Monster Tidbits" bonus chapter.

Shizuku Hayama is the personal bodyguard for Ichika Kiryuin, the only daughter of a major industrialist. But Ichika is no shrinking violet, and she's perfectly able to handle any dangerous situation or challenge by herself. If Ichika doesn't need anyone protect her body, maybe Shizuku can help to protect her heart?
